description: Anders Tegnell says more should have been done early on to stem coronavirus in Sweden.
title: Coronavirus: Sweden's Tegnell admits too many died
title_page: Coronavirus: Sweden's Tegnell admits too many died - BBC News
maintext: Now he has told Swedish public radio: "If we were to encounter the same disease again, knowing exactly what we know about it today, I think we would settle on doing something in between what Sweden did and what the rest of the world has done."
